extendedInfo.description: The perfect app for Pomeranian dog owners, or indeed any dog lover. This app includes images of sable, white, black, and mixed coloring pommies. The pomeranian is a cute toy dog belonging to the Spitz family. The images included in this app will look wonderful as a background on your device.Over 30 high-quality images are included in this app, and more will be added, keep checking for new ones.Please understand some ads will be displayed within our apps to help support continued development.
